text: Jacob Dylan "Jake" Wood (born July 12, 1972) is an English actor, voice artist, and comedian. He is best known for playing Max Branning in EastEnders and in the United States as the current voice of the GEICO gecko. ==Other websites== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from London Category:English comedians
